<image mime-type="image/jpeg" src="../../media/OSC_Astro_06_06_Conception.jpg"/>
</media>
<caption>The primary mirror in this telescope is 39.3 meters across. The telescope is under construction in the Atacama Desert in Northern Chile. (credit: ESO/L. Calçada)</caption>
